    <h3 {...{
      "id": "linux-531-kernel"
    }}>{`LINUX-5.3.1: Kernel`}</h3>
    <p>{`The Linux Kernel is a Unix-like OS.`}</p>
    <p>{`The Linux is the core of any Linux installation.`}</p>
    <p>{`The Linux kernel is responsible for managing every other piece of software on a running Linux computer.`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`It is responsibile for all of the interfacing of all the applications down to hardware between the interprocess communication system.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Provides critical low level tasks.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Loaded very early on in the boot process.`}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>{`We could change the program that runs as the first process by adding it to the boot loader option command line.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`# run bash first after boot
